<% provide(:title, 'About Us') %>
<div class="center hero-unit">
	<h1>We locate stickers!</h1><br/>
  <div class="row-fluid">
  <div class="span7">
		<p>
			LocateMyStickers is a simple and complete geolocation solution.
		<p>
		</p>
			If you get tired of losing your precious things, or wonder where your cat goes during the day? Think about us!
		</p>
		<p>
			We provide little stickers that will permit you to <b>track whatever you want</b>.
			Stick it, and follow the way your sticker will take through our iOs, Android and web applications!
		</p>
	</div>
  <div class="span3 offset1">
	  <%= image_tag 'lmslogo_400.png' %>
	</div>
	</div>
<br/>
	<p class='lead'>
		<b>Is'nt that awesome, for us head-in-the-clouds? :)</b>
	</p>
</div>
<div class="center hero-unit">
	<h1>Who we are</h1><br/>
	<div class="row-fluid">
		<ul class="thumbnails">
			<% @admins.each do |admin| %>
			  <li>
			  	<a href="<%= user_path(admin) %>">
						<%= gravatar_for admin, size: 128, class: "user-pin" %>
			  	</a>
			  </li>
		  <% end %>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<p>
		We are a team of seven developers driven by the thought that geolocation, today, remains not as accessible and used as it should.
	</p>
	<p>
		We take our time to produce a solution that provides an easy, efficient, and free way to locate one's personnal belongings.
	</p><br/>
	<p class='lead'>
		We need your advices! Please <%= link_to "contact us!", contact_path %> and share your idea of what such a solution should be :)
	</p>
</div>
<div class="center hero-unit">
	<h1>The web application</h1><br/>
	<p class='lead'>
		You are on the LocateMyStickers Web application. LocateMyStickers is also available on iOs and Android.
	</p><br/>
	<p><%= image_tag 'shema-web-service.png', class: 'img-rounded' %></p>
</div>
